422
It shows the trend of the token currently open on the chart for 5m, 15m, 30m, 1h, 2h, 4h, 6h, 12h, 1d, 1w, and 1 month (displayed in the table on the right).

It indicates when all of them are either green (a total uptrend) or red (a total downtrend).
